  "instructions": [
    "Soak red lentils overnight in water",
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat",
    "Add diced onion and garlic; sauté until soft",
    "Stir in smoked paprika, cumin, and tomato paste; cook for 1 minute",
    "Add soaked lentils, red food coloring, water, and bay leaf",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low; cover and simmer for 25 minutes",
    "Remove bay leaf; stir in salt and pepper to taste",
    "Simmer uncovered for 5 minutes to thicken"
